@startuml report-merge-model-detail
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

title **[2/4] Model merge** — signals, questions, context tiers

left to right direction

package "From prev report" #FFF8E1 {
  component "signalReasons arrays" as PR
  component "questions" as PQ
  component "hi / medium / lowContext" as PC
  component "signal levels (D max later)" as PS
}

package "From next group G_k" #E3F2FD {
  component "signalReasons (strings)" as GR
  component "questions" as GQ
  component "hi / medium / lowContext" as GC
  component "signal levels" as GS
}

package "Merge result (M:r + D)" #FFF3E0 {
  component "**Levels (D):**\nmax(prev, group)\nper dimension" as OUTS
  component "**Reasons (M:r):**\narray = merge + dedupe" as OUTR
  component "**Questions (M:r):**\nrecompute, dedupe,\nrole-valuable picks" as OUTQ
  component "**Context tiers (M:r):**\nmerge bullets,\ndemote-only rank,\ncap 12/tier" as OUTC
}

PR --> OUTR
GR --> OUTR
PQ --> OUTQ
GQ --> OUTQ
PC --> OUTC
GC --> OUTC
PS --> OUTS
GS --> OUTS

note bottom of OUTQ
  Targets gaps Git still cannot know.
  Drops duplicates and questions already
  answered by project context / story.
end note

note bottom of OUTC
  NEVER promote a bullet to higher tier.
  Routine upkeep -> one generic low bullet.
  Least important dropped when over cap.
end note

@enduml


