H3 --> H2b
S2 --> S2b : **union** group files
S3 --> S2b

note bottom
  Cursor moves **round the list** (wrap to 0),
  so compaction spreads across ages — not always
  squashing the same oldest blob.
  **Newest entry is never the first merged.**
  Next fold: cursor = 3 (or 0 if wrapped).
end note

